title: Grateful Dead Live at Poplar Creek Music Theatre on 1983-06-28
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Dire Wolf, It's All Over Now, Brown Eyed Women, Little Red Rooster, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain-> Deal

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Iko Iko

reviews.review_text: Great AUD recording Tour-ender. Party powder show for sure (FAST tempos on everything). Massive setlist and great performances of all the songs. Sweet-sounding tape.
